      <p class="text-justify">This Privacy Policy provides information about the collection, use, and disclosure of Personal Information upon usage of EZKHATA applications & website. You are advised to read this Privacy Policy carefully. By downloading and using the EZKHATA application / website you expressly give us consent to use & disclose your personal information in accordance with this Privacy Policy. </p>
   
   <p class="text-justify"><b>Note:</b> Our privacy policy may change at any time without prior notification. To make sure that you are aware of any changes, kindly review the policy periodically. This Privacy Policy shall apply uniformly to EZKHATA applications & website.</p>
