  <div class="row">
   <div class="col-md-12">
   <h3>General</h3>
   <p class="text-justify">We will not sell, share or rent your personal information to any 3rd party or use your contact details for unsolicited emails and / or SMS. Any emails and / or SMS sent by EZKHATA will only be in connection with the provision of agreed services & products and this Privacy Policy. We may periodically reveal general statistical information about EZKHATA & its users, such as number of visitors, number and type of goods and services purchased, etc.</p>
   
   <p class="text-justify">We reserve the right to communicate your personal information to any third party that makes a legally-compliant request for its disclosure.</p>
   </div>
 </div>
 
 
 <div class="row">
   <div class="col-md-12">
   <h3>Personal Information</h3>
   <p class="text-justify">While using EZKHATA applications & website, we may ask you to provide us with certain identifiable information that can be used to contact or identify you. Personal Information means and includes all information that can be linked to a specific individual or to identify any individual, such as name, residential address, mailing address, telephone number, Aadhaar Card, PAN Number, email ID, photo, biometric information, bank account details etc. Any other information voluntarily provided by the user in connection with availing any of the services on EZKHATA will also be considered as personal information. We will also access your navigational log and correspondence information/data to help us analyze merchants, markets, technology, operating systems, browsers, devices, locations from which EZKHATA services are used. </p>
   </div>
 </div>
 
 <div class="row">
   <div class="col-md-12">
   <h3>Use of Personal Information</h3>
   <p class="text-justify">We use your personal information to provide you with services & products you explicitly requested for, to resolve disputes, troubleshoot concerns, help promote safe services, collect money, measure consumer interest in our services, customize your experience, detect & protect us against error, fraud and other criminal activity, enforce our terms and conditions, etc.
This information can also be used to identify and / or contact you to inform about offers, products, services, updates etc.</p>
  
   <p class="text-justify">We may occasionally ask you to complete optional online surveys to gather contact information and demographic information (like zip code, age, gender, etc.). This data will be used to customize your experience at EZKHATA, providing you with content that we think you might be interested in and to display content according to your preferences.</p>
   </div>
 </div>
 
 <div class="row">
   <div class="col-md-12">
   <h3>Cookies</h3>
   <p class="text-justify">Cookies are files with small amount of data that is commonly used an anonymous unique identifier. These are sent to your browser from the website that you visit and are stored on your computer’s hard drive. EZKHATA uses these ‘cookies’ to collect information and improve our services. Aggregate cookie may be shared with third parties.</p>
   </div>
 </div>
 
 <div class="row">
   <div class="col-md-12">
